5 THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED that the Legislature of Louisiana does hereby
6 commend John Keith of AllState Land and Timber on being named Louisiana Outstanding
7 Logger of the Year; does hereby recognize his steadfast dedication and commitment to the
8 logging industry; and does hereby extend enduring appreciation for his tireless efforts
9 performing safe and efficient logging practices that benefit Louisiana's environment and
10 economy.
